name: Teia Logo Studies - Video
description:
Digital Video, 4200 x 2300 px, 49 seconds, 30 fps, no sound. 

Created February-March 2022. 


Shared in anticipation of 700,000 OBJKTs minted. 

Part of my process to create a series of "Turbulent Determinism" style logos for teia. The word "TEIA" was written in 10 different fonts, and this was used as a shape/filter layer, as in the heart, star, and chaos/order videos. This clip shows a portion of the resulting video, with some added effects. Modified black & white versions of 3 of these logos currently are part of the teia logo rotation.  


Generative artwork created procedurally in Photoshop using custom macros and scripts. Post processing in After Effects.
